org.shininet.bukkit.playerheads

Enum LegacySkullType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LegacySkullType>
      • org.shininet.bukkit.playerheads.LegacySkullType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<LegacySkullType>
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public enum LegacySkullType
extends Enum<LegacySkullType>
    Defines an enum of Username-based Skulls (playerheads) associated with mobs. (Previously named CustomSkullType) Each skull may be associated with multiple usernames for the purposes of recognizing and updating heads, but only one is used for spawning new heads. This enum does not include mobs supported by vanilla skulltypes. Note: This documentation was inferred after the fact and may be inaccurate.
    Author:
    meiskam
    See Also:
    SkullType
